Capital Markets

Company Overview of Gratia Capital, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Gratia Capital, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It invests in the public equity markets across the globe with a focus on United States. The firm invests in value stocks of companies. It also employs event-oriented and opportunistic strategy. The firm uses fundamental analysis to make its investments. The firm combines in-house and external research to make its investments. It typically invests in companies in consumer, industrials, and real estate sectors. Gratia Capital, LLC was founded in April 2012 and is based in Los Angeles, California.


2029 Century Park EastSuite 1180Los Angeles, CA 90067United StatesFounded in 2012



